text: JK says the #FACup is a massive competition. It‚Äôs the first experience of playing in a semi-final in the competition but it‚Äôs better late than never. He adds that he hopes the fans get to Wembley safely and create a good atmosphere #MCILIV #LFC

text: Klopp on the #FACup "It's a massive competition. Obviously so far we couldn't get to the semis yet so a first experience in the semi-final but better late than never... I hope we have the atmosphere a semi-final between Liverpool and City deserves" #LFC #MCFC

author: BBC Sport Merseyside
text: JK says they have to treat the game as a ‚Äòfinal‚Äô and they have to treat every game between now and the end of the season in the same way #LFC #MCFC #MCILIV #FACup

author: Liverpool FC news

text: JK says they know about the quality of #MCFC - there are decisive challenges throughout the game and #LFC need to win them. It‚Äôs a really intense fight on a really high level. It‚Äôs similar to the #EFLCup final against #CFC #MCILIV #FACup
